Channel activity of the top 80% globally¶

This section shows the same channel activity results, but limited only to the list of top users who, server-wide, contribute 80% of all messages on the server. In other words, this shows where our most active users spend their time.

This is distinct from the top 80% shown in the previous section, which is calculated on a channel-by-channel basis.
